reviewText: Just ok dvd with a bunch of short clips of vendors and such. Doesn't really show the wild side. Needs to be a little more raunchy for my tastes!
good movie showing pieces of different rallies. definitely work the price
Good Movie of Sturgis. Does a good job of showing the event that everyone can't go to see in person.
I was duped into watching this due to a 5 star review on Amazon.  IT was no where near the cool documentaries about motorcycle culture at all.
If you enjoy the biker world then you will love this movie . It has a lot of good footage of all the major rallies .
